    <string name="donate_title">Want to buy me a beer?</string>
    <string name="donate_head">Donations are always appreciated and helpful in funding the future development of this and other apps.\n\nIf you find Hangar useful and want to show thanks for the work that has gone into it, feel free to leave a review reflecting your experience with the app, or if you\'re in a generous mood, you can donate using <b>Google Play</b> or <b>PayPal</b> below.</string>
